{"tid":235374,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登某部份盲目仇女既撚屌已經去到唔可以唔正視","createTime":"2017-05-09T03:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T05:23:48.000Z","uid":18720,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cfe64470b0cff39ded933677c54540c31dcd51b9","tid":235374,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:24:27.000Z","msg":"quote from小王子的星球巴打<br />\n<br />\n想像一個肥矮柒喺一間不足50呎嘅公屋房入面<br />\n右手一邊留言話港女係雞係公廁<br />\n左手揸住已經被佢肚腩遮住嘅短鳩<br />\n一路劣一路用把肥豬聲喃喃自語：<br />\n「咪又雞 臭閪港女 嫁去德國做德國雞 我屌撚死你啊」<br />\n6秒後 喺地下隨手執起尋晚用過紙巾抹下子孫根<br />\n慢慢托一托副啊伯眼鏡 頓覺心情舒暢<br />\n因為佢覺得頭先已經侮辱得港女淋離盡至 直情可以影響到佢嘅幸福 幫港男出返啖氣！"},{"pid":"7f32322490d9a18decc5495ad9c42d9233662ee6","tid":235374,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:25:46.000Z","msg":"標題漏左字自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到唔可以唔正視既地步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e1fe8fdd59511fa7e565a0777f8822b565fcc2","tid":235374,"uid":17928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:27:21.000Z","msg":"樓主的一生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b2f6afca8ecf09580104f8146d9d6b1eb2534a","tid":235374,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7gCfoA0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7gCfoA0.jpg&h=7b71a415&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1c4436728f6bce55c82045bf936b3849f83cac9","tid":235374,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b50ad596e805696bcd628dc6890073bec94de3","tid":235374,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:55:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主的一生<img s